For the moment let's ignore annual structure and just collapse this into timeseries sampled bimonthly.  


```r
require(reshape2)
dt <- melt(dat, id="YEAR")
X <- dt$value
Z <- X[!is.na(X)]
Z <- data.frame(1:(length(Z)-1), Z[1:(length(Z)-1)])
```



```r
png("mei.png")
require(earlywarnings)
a <- generic_ews(Z, detrending="gaussian")
```
